Jul 06 11:32:54 odroid-hc1 electrumx_server.py[18601]: INFO:BlockProcessor:tx/sec since genesis: 84, since last flush: 23
Jul 06 11:32:54 odroid-hc1 electrumx_server.py[18601]: INFO:BlockProcessor:sync time: 41d 11h 26m  ETA: 16d 17h 03m
Jul 06 11:45:45 odroid-hc1 electrumx_server.py[18601]: INFO:BlockProcessor:our height: 512,366 daemon: 530,692 UTXOs 295MB hist 9MB
Jul 06 11:59:12 odroid-hc1 electrumx_server.py[18601]: INFO:BlockProcessor:our height: 512,378 daemon: 530,695 UTXOs 302MB hist 23MB
```

Disk utilsation is pretty rought:
```
# iostat -cdxm
Linux 4.9.0-6-armmp-lpae (odroid-hc1)   07/06/2018      _armv7l_        (8 CPU)

avg-cpu:  %user   %nice %system %iowait  %steal   %idle
           1.47    0.44    0.75   13.25    0.00   84.09

