7709,IssuesEvent,2016-03-24 07:26:32+00:00,613742,basho/riak-python-client,1639570,daroot,176293,basho,opened,Inconsistent datatype reload() behavior between PBC and HTTP.,[],[],0,"Python 2.7, using riak-python-client 2.4.2:

