8818,IssuesEvent,2018-08-23 15:14:11+00:00,36200353,candango/firenado,715641,piraz,715660,candango,opened,The configuration file stream is opened for a while after we load the yaml file.,"[{'id': 215675728, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwyMTU2NzU3Mjg=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/candango/firenado/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'fc2929', 'default': True}]","[{'login': 'piraz', 'id': 715641, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjcxNTY0MQ==', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/715641?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/piraz', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/piraz/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"The load_yaml_config_file function in the config.py is not closing the file stream after we load the yaml to the memory.

