        return render_template('contacts/list.html', contacts=contacts)
```

This doesn't work as ListView is not the method, but moving the decorator I get
`BuildError: ('contacts.get', {}, None)` which figures as I think I want 'contacts.Listview.get'.

Thoughts?
",{},{}
