9468,IssuesEvent,2017-10-13 11:48:34+00:00,37842598,inveniosoftware/invenio-jsonschemas,4287772,drjova,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,docs: add a Warning recommending not to store or advertise invenio-jsonschema URLs,"[{'id': 227365034, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio-jsonschemas/labels/Type:%20enhancement', 'name': 'Type: enhancement', 'color': 'ff5500', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'switowski', 'id': 4835412, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/4835412?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/switowski', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/switowski/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"Related to the discussion in inveniosoftware/invenio-records#117

**Problem Description**:
- records are versioned and can be reverted to a previous version.
- URLs can always change, be it the hostname or the API.

Thus we need to store references to JSON-Schemas as stable URLs. Example: DOI/EPIC/...

**Solution:**
We should add a warning in the documentation mentioning that we don't recommend storing invenio-jsonschema URLs directly in records. A more stable URI should be used.
",{},{}
