9999,IssuesEvent,2017-06-08 16:16:09+00:00,2527828,getsentry/raven-python,23610,dcramer,1396951,getsentry,closed,Is raven_compat needed anymore?,[],[],1,"All the docs seem to reference imports as e.g.:

