11002,IssuesEvent,2017-03-01 17:25:30+00:00,6248645,ARM-DOE/pyart,1050278,jjhelmus,2540600,ARM-DOE,closed,Python 3.6 Incompatibility with pyart.correct.despeckle_field,[],[],2,"While running pyart on python 3.6 I encountered this problem:

