11040,IssuesEvent,2016-02-17 21:43:51+00:00,7804703,testing-cabal/testtools,372783,thomir,2662570,testing-cabal,opened,`raises` matcher Mismatch text could be more helpful,[],[],0,"I often write test code like so:

