Wed Oct 12 19:07:27 2016 kern.err ss-redir[3746]: server recv: Connection reset by peer

I tried to diagnose on my server side but I doubt it can come from me as I didn't change anything on my configuration since a few weeks already (and I'm the only one using this server).
