 RID:         osx.10.12-x64
 Base Path:   /usr/local/share/dotnet/sdk/2.1.4/

Microsoft .NET Core Shared Framework Host

  Version  : 2.0.5
  Build    : 17373eb129b3b05aa18ece963f8795d65ef8ea54 
```

The build error happens on this machine (Mac OS X) as well as Windows 10 x64
 
Thanks

[BugReport.zip](https://github.com/dotnet/core/files/1690432/BugReport.zip)",{},{}
