15110,IssuesEvent,2016-07-17 07:57:09+00:00,14284859,marshmallow-code/marshmallow,6513121,alexpantyukhin,10334301,marshmallow-code,opened,Question about customize of deep populating Schema.,[],[],0,"Hi.

