15673,IssuesEvent,2017-09-20 19:27:51+00:00,99273369,NeurodataWithoutBorders/pynwb,219043,jcfr,12140348,NeurodataWithoutBorders,opened,Create appveyor team to setup continuous integration,"[{'id': 661457898, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/NeurodataWithoutBorders/pynwb/labels/task', 'name': 'task', 'color': 'ededed', 'default': False}]",[],0,"In order to have a Appveyor organization named ""NeurodataWithoutBorders"", 


