15703,IssuesEvent,2015-06-12 12:07:23+00:00,6704888,django-import-export/django-import-export,13813,bmihelac,12345453,django-import-export,closed,IntegerWidget clean() returns None when value is 0,[],[],8,"I've been having problems importing data and found this problem. I don't know if it's an issue with django-import-export (0.2.6), Python (2.7.6), or my postgres (9.1.14) schema. I'm using Django 1.7.

