16866,IssuesEvent,2016-08-30 22:43:03+00:00,55147386,tflearn/tflearn,3070132,tuming1990,16848261,tflearn,opened,"""Coordinator stopped with threads still running"" happens when using cross-validation",[],[],0,"Hi,

