18058,IssuesEvent,2018-04-08 16:42:43+00:00,23465887,pdfminer/pdfminer.six,7139697,WtfJoke,22586632,pdfminer,opened,Wrong PDF Text Order ,[],[],0,"I want to extract the text of this pdf: [Wochenkarte-KW-15-Neu.pdf](https://github.com/pdfminer/pdfminer.six/files/1887670/Wochenkarte-KW-15-Neu.pdf)

